You're sure?

105
00:05:28,510 --> 00:05:29,550
Shirase!

106
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:31,060
Shirase-chan!

107
00:05:31,280 --> 00:05:32,490
You did it!

108
00:05:34,570 --> 00:05:36,810
Yes... Yes!

109
00:05:37,750 --> 00:05:38,850
Yes!

110
00:05:39,110 --> 00:05:42,980
Well? Told you, didn't I? I told you 
that my plan would work perfectly!

111
00:05:42,220 --> 00:05:42,980
But...

112
00:05:42,980 --> 00:05:45,550
