At last, Antarctica!

116
00:05:49,900 --> 00:05:50,910
Wait for me, penguins!

117
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:52,490
Wait for me, auroras!

118
00:05:55,370 --> 00:05:56,620
I bet that hurt.

119
00:05:56,950 --> 00:05:58,590
Sorry, she's an idiot.

120
00:05:58,590 --> 00:05:59,460
