123
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:07,380
I'm borrowing your sandals.

124
00:06:07,380 --> 00:06:08,240
Excuse me.

125
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,510
Wait!

126
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:18,560
Hello there.

127
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:23,440
New Dosanko Promotions
Producer, Manager
Shiraishi Tamiko

128
00:06:20,460 --> 00:06:23,440
I am Yuzuki's manager.

129
00:06:23,910 --> 00:06:26,060
My name is Shiraishi Tamiko.

130
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:28,480
Shiraishi?

131
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:29,700
I am also her mother.

132
00:06:30,030 --> 00:06:31,300
Thought so.

133
00:06:31,300 --> 00:06:33,700
I keep telling you, I'm not going.

134
00:06:33,900 --> 00:06:36,700
But you have to go. 
It's your job, remember?

135
00:06:37,030 --> 00:06:39,780
I told these girls they could do it instead.

136
00:06:39,780 --> 00:06:43,290
Do you really think it's 
your place to decide that?

137
00:06:41,210 --> 00:06:42,840
TV Program Outline
High School Girl Goes to Antarctica!

138
00:06:43,290 --> 00:06:43,960
